#: ../../platform/overview.rst:2
msgid "Platform Overview"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:4
msgid "DeePAW is an online inference service platform for the DeePAW method, offering both a web interface and a RESTful API. It is designed to provide materials science researchers with efficient, high-throughput charge density calculation services."
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:7
msgid "Core Features"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:9
msgid "**Batch charge density prediction**: Predicts three-dimensional charge density distributions from atomic structure files"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:10
msgid "**Multi-format file support**: Supports 15 structure file formats including CIF, VASP, XYZ, and PDB"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:11
msgid "**Multi-GPU parallel scheduling**: Built-in priority queue and GPU task scheduler supporting concurrent multi-task execution"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:12
msgid "**RESTful API**: Comprehensive programmatic access interface for seamless integration into automated workflows"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:13
msgid "**CHGCAR output**: VASP-compatible format, directly visualizable with tools such as VESTA and Ovito"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:14
msgid "**Real-time progress tracking**: Live task status updates delivered via WebSocket"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:15
msgid "**Web frontend**: React-based interactive interface with 3D isosurface visualization"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:16
msgid "**Model warm-start**: GPU model caching mechanism that keeps the model resident in VRAM after the first inference, eliminating repeated loading overhead for subsequent tasks"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:19
msgid "Technology Stack"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:21
msgid "**Frontend**: React 19 + TypeScript + Vite + Plotly.js"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:22
msgid "**Backend**: FastAPI + Uvicorn (ASGI)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:23
msgid "**Inference**: PyTorch + E3NN + ASE"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:24
msgid "**Data format**: Multiple formats -> ASE Database -> CHGCAR (VASP)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:27
msgid "System Architecture"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:41
msgid "GPU Task Scheduling"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:43
msgid "One worker thread per GPU, with exclusive access enforced via ``threading.Lock``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:44
msgid "Tasks are processed in order of a priority queue (PriorityQueue)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:45
msgid "Model caching: the first task loads the model into GPU VRAM (~5-10 s); subsequent tasks reuse the cached instance (<0.1 s overhead)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:46
msgid "One model instance cached per GPU, occupying approximately 2-4 GB of VRAM"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:49
msgid "System Requirements"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:52
msgid "Server Side"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:54
msgid "Python 3.10+"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:55
msgid "CUDA 11.8+ / 12.x"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:56
msgid "GPU: 8 GB+ VRAM (16 GB+ recommended)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:57
msgid "Disk: approximately 5-10 MB per CHGCAR file"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:58
msgid "Memory: 16 GB+ (32 GB+ recommended)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:61
msgid "Client Side"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:63
msgid "Python 3.7+ (only the ``requests`` library required)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:64
msgid "Or any programming language with HTTP request support"
msgstr ""

#: ../../platform/overview.rst:65
msgid "No GPU requirement"
msgstr ""
